{"service_name": "Establish an Information Security role in a Design Authority", "service_id": "5658118897795072", "company_name": "Corix Partners Technical Services Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Corix Partners Technical Services Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Establish an Information Security role in a Design Authority\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    The service, from Corix Partners, reviews the existing governance structure in order to create and establish an Information Security role within the existing Design Authority.\r\n\r\nExpertise can be provided to fill the Information Security role in the Design Authority, including coaching staff members to fulfil this role in the future.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Identifying an appropriate Design Authority within the existing governance structure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defining the Information Security role within Design Authority\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Working with key stakeholders to establish the Information Security role\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establish Design Authority with key stakeholders, if one doesn\u2019t exist\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Act as the Information Security specialist on Design Authority\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Clear, well defined role for Information Security within Design Authority\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensuring that Information Security requirements are properly considered and implemented\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reviews throughout both project and solution lifecycles\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highlight potential Information Security consequences\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Clear understanding of any exceptions highlighted by Design Authority\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides Information Security expertise on Design Authority\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent assessment by expert professionals with real-life field experience\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a31000 to \u00a32000 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585604/5658118897795072-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585604/5658118897795072-sfia-rate-card-2015-04-28-1520.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585604/5658118897795072-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n     